---
title: HelloHero: Spiced Halloumi & Jewel Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Eat the tropical rainbow tonight with this vibrant collection of veggies and halloumi cooked in our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning. We’re keeping those beach vibes going by adding a charred pineapple slaw, coconut sauce and a hint of nutty peanuts.

